umcimbi: Nantoni na ethatha indawo kwaye inobunzima
isiqalelo: Into ecocekileyo eyenziwe ngohlobo olunye kuphela lwe-athomu
athom: Iyunithi encinci yenkqunto enokuthi ithathe inxaxheba kwi-chemical reaction
ikhompawundi: Into eyenziwe ngezinto ezimbini nangaphezulu ezidityaniswe ngokwekhemikhali
umxube: Ukudityaniswa kwezinto ezimbini nangaphezulu ezingadityaniswanga ngokwekhemikhali
ifanayo: Umxube kunye nokwakheka okufanayo kuyo yonke indawo (umzekelo, isisombululo)
urhulumente: Uhlobo apho umba okhoyo (oqinileyo, ulwelo, igesi, iplasma)
eqinileyo: Imeko yento enemilo echanekileyo kunye nomthamo
ulwelo: Imeko yento enomthamo oqinisekileyo kodwa akukho milo iqinisekileyo
igesi: Ubume bemiba engenamilo iqinisekileyo okanye umthamo
ukusabela: Inkqubo apho izinto zitshintsha ukuze zenze izinto ezintsha
ibhondi: Ukunyanzelela ukubamba iiathom kunye kwimolekyuli okanye ikhompawundi
ifomula yemichiza: Indlela emfutshane yokumela into kusetyenziswa iisimboli kunye namanani
isisombululo: Umxube we-solute (into enyibilikisiweyo) kunye ne-solvent (into enyibilikayo)
ugxininiso: Isixa sesolute esinyityilisiweyo kwisixa esinikiweyo sesinyibilikisi
ukungathathi hlangothi: Ukusabela phakathi kwe-asidi kunye nesiseko, ukwenza ityuwa kunye namanzi
amandla ekhemikhali: Amandla anokubakho agcinwe kwiibhondi zekhemikhali zento
